          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "This method is called just before a contextual menu for a view is opened on screen. It provides an opportunity to make any desired changes to the visual state of the view. For example, a table view might select a row in response to the contextual menu being displayed."
